                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND

              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e

[2019/05/13 09:57:26] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist

                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 10:38:23] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan

                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 10:48:47] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   p.prom_costo, p.prom_duracion,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 11:18:47] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 11:23:17] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

[2019/05/13 11:29:29] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC
[2019/05/13 11:29:29] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.promocional, p.num_cuenta, p.num_accesos, p.limite_perfiles,
                   p.prom_costo, p.prom_duracion,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest,

                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

[2019/05/13 11:40:26] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC
[2019/05/13 11:40:26] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.promocional, p.num_cuenta, p.num_accesos, p.limite_perfiles,
                   p.prom_costo, p.prom_duracion,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo,

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 11:54:20] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga,

            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND

            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 12:45:21] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 12:49:04] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

[2019/05/13 01:04:26] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist

                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest,

                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga,

                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan

                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest,

                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 2 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest

                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e

[2019/05/13 01:14:22] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC
[2019/05/13 01:14:22] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.promocional, p.num_cuenta, p.num_accesos, p.limite_perfiles,
                   p.prom_costo, p.prom_duracion,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga,

            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan

[2019/05/13 01:17:53] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.costo, e.id_comprobante,e.id_empresa_plan_parent, e.fecha_compra,        
                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC
[2019/05/13 01:17:53] SQL Query: SELECT p.id_plan, p.nombre, p.promocional, p.num_cuenta, p.num_accesos, p.limite_perfiles,
                   p.prom_costo, p.prom_duracion,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_codigo_paypal,p.codigo_paypal) AS codigo_paypal,
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_num_post,p.num_post) AS num_post, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_costo,p.costo) AS costo, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_duracion,p.duracion) AS duracion, 
                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo = 0 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo

                     IFNULL(e.fecha_caducidad,'-') AS fecha_caducidad, 
                     CASE WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_publicaciones_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_publicaciones_rest
                     END AS num_post_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_descarga_rest = -1 THEN 'ilimitado'
                          WHEN num_descarga_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_descarga_rest
                     END AS num_descarga_rest, 
                     CASE WHEN num_accesos_rest IS NULL THEN '-'
                          WHEN num_accesos_rest = 0 THEN '-'
                          ELSE num_accesos_rest
                     END AS num_accesos_rest,
                     e.id_empresa_plan AS id_usuario_plan, e.estado, f.id_factura
              FROM mfo_empresa_plan e
              INNER JOIN mfo_plan p ON e.id_plan = p.id_plan
              LEFT JOIN mfo_factura f ON f.id_user_emp_plan = e.id_empresa_plan AND 
                                         f.tipo_usuario = 2 AND f.estado = 2
              WHERE e.id_empresa = '1' AND
                    (e.estado = 1 OR (e.estado = 0 AND e.id_comprobante <> '')) ORDER BY e.fecha_compra ASC

                   IF(p.promocional,p.prom_porc_descarga,p.porc_descarga) AS porc_descarga, 
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.descripcion ORDER BY e.orden) AS permisos,
                   GROUP_CONCAT(a.accion ORDER BY e.orden) AS acciones
            FROM mfo_plan p
            INNER JOIN mfo_permisoplan e ON p.id_plan = e.id_plan  
            INNER JOIN mfo_accionsist a ON e.id_accionSist = a.id_accionSist            
            WHERE p.tipo_usuario = '2' AND p.estado = 1 AND p.id_sucursal = '1' AND 
                  a.estado = 1 AND p.visibilidad = 1  AND p.costo <> 0  AND p.tipo_plan = 1 GROUP BY p.id_plan ORDER BY p.costo
